BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:🔍 Choose Your Path Timed Research
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Brussels:20260505T100000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Brussels:20260512T200000
DTSTAMP:20260512T082525Z
UID:2026-05-05T10:00:00+02:00-6227887906952138264@leekduck-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Niantic is testing a new branching Timed Research format durin
 g “evergreen weeks\,” which are weeks without major events where seaso
 nal gameplay takes focus.\n\nThis Timed Research lets you choose your own 
 way to play for the week by selecting one of three branches based on explo
 ration\, skill\, or battling.\n\nChoose wisely! You can select only one pa
 th and remain on that path until the end of the Timed Research.\n\nEach pa
 th grants a different event bonus and includes different tasks and rewards
 .\n\nMore info: https://leekduck.com/events/choose-your-path-timed-researc
 h/\n\nData from LeekDuck.com
LOCATION:Pokemon GO
URL:https://leekduck.com/events/choose-your-path-timed-research/
